{htxt id="custommosaico_brand_fonts_select"}
  {ts}
  Specify your organisation's brand fonts. They will appear as options in the font selection box on the Mosaico compose mailing screen. You should add each brand font separately as options, only the name of the font is required in the Label and Value field i.e. Lato or Montserrat, and it is case-sensitive.
  {/ts}
